PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans of ROBERT KRISTJANSON, of Gimli, Manitoba, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of William Monkman, whose term has expired.
